name: My favorite swappers swaps
description: This tool lets you find the last swaps by your favorite swappers (artists or collectors). To adapt it to your needs you have to download the svg file from ipfs (the last line in this page), save it as myFavs.svg, open it with a text editor, add your favorite swappers wallet addresses to the myFavSwappers list (around line 30), save the file and open it again with a web browser.
